Content: Don't be misled by the title; this isn't just about herbs and vitamins. With a list of contributors that reads like a "Who's Who" of natural medicine, this superb guide thoroughly covers clinically proven natural treatments for most common medical conditions. An easy-to-use, valuable resource for consumers and practitioners alike. Recommended.
